main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 702/2001 is amended as follows:
1. in Article 1 "of 47000 tonnes of common wheat" is replaced by "of 144636 tonnes of common wheat";
2. Article 2(2) is replaced by the following: "2. The final date for the submission of tenders for the last partial invitation to tender shall expire on 27 June 2001."
